parameters: Please make sure to write a thorough report.
I see... So there is an empire in hell.

Damn... There are so many powerful individuals...
Even I am barely hanging on.

I'm glad... It seems like I was able to defeat it
with my weak magic...

Don't worry, I'll call someone who can provide
immediate medical treatment.
It seems like it's finally settled.
But, there are so many injured people...

(What is their purpose? I wonder if they're after
Leviathan's magical power.)

It seems that the appearance of monsters is not
limited to just the Grand Library.

They have been appearing all over the academy, and
the faculty and students are cooperating to fight
back.

Vice President Olivia is taking turns to suppress
them, so I think they will be settled soon.

Masamune-san seems to be at his limit. Let's leave
this to Vice President Olivia.
I won't be defeated by something of this level.

You wouldn't honestly answer such a question,
would you?

Besides, it doesn't matter. You all will become
sacrifices from now on.

Performing a black mass and gathering magical
power.

And I will fulfill the family's long-cherished
desire!
I won't let you do such a thing...
Hehe... Then try to stop me.

(If the black mass starts, there's nothing I can
do anymore)

There are various books here, it's fun. Masamune-
san, you need to write your report properly too.

Haa, haa... I guess I'm more of a beast than a
human after all.
I see... So there is an empire in hell.
